description: IDEX Biometrics ASA, together with its subsidiaries, designs, develops, and sells fingerprint authentication solutions in Norway, Europe, the Middle East, Africa, the Americas, and the Asia-Pacific regions. The company's fingerprint authentication solutions are used primarily in contactless smart cards that includes financial payment, access control, and digital identity, as well as card-based devices for the storage of digital currencies. It offers IDEX digital access card a multifactor authentication solution; IDEX pay card; IDEX bio java card platform, a fingerprint biometric authentication solution; and IDEX Bio sensor system for biometric algorithms and proprietary silicon technology. It primarily serves smart card manufacturers and similar solution integrators. The company was incorporated in 1996 and is headquartered in Oslo, Norway.
